main event: A red, circular UFO was observed over northwest Baltimore, Maryland in 1963.
interesting points: The UFO was sighted by a woman named Mrs. Virginia Garrison and her 14-year-old son Sidney Ingram.
The UFO was observed traveling in a westerly direction at an estimated altitude of 2,300 feet.
Friendship Airport in the area reported no aircraft down and no other sightings or reports received.
The report notes that the sighting occurred at 2317242Z (11:17 PM EDT).
The report indicates that the sighting was a 'visual sighting' by the witnesses.
witnesses: Mrs. Virginia Garrison and her 14-year-old son Sidney Ingram
